   ;;  Shortcut	Function
   ;;  Tab Or C-i	Next Item
   ;;  Shift-Tab	Previous Item
   ;;  Return / Mouse Click / C-m	Open
   ;;  r	Recent files
   ;;  m	Bookmarks
   ;;  p	Projects
